<h1>Grigson Font Explorer</h1>
<p class="meta">Per-font glyph tables for fonts used in the Grigson project.</p>

<ul>
  {% for font in fontPages %}
    <li><a href="/{{ font.slug }}/">{{ font.name }}</a> — {{ font.totalGlyphs }} glyphs ({{ font.outline }}, {{ font.upm }} UPM)</li>
  {% endfor %}
</ul>
